source.name: International Energy Statistics
source.description: Country specific data by year, month and quarter.  Most data are available back to 1980. Fuel production, consumption, imports, exports, capacity, stocks, emissions, heat contents, and conversion factors; as well as population, as available for all fuels and countries.
